# Controller Integration Tests Style

- Use full-context tests with `@SpringBootTest` and `@AutoConfigureMockMvc`.
- Reset state each test with `@DirtiesContext(BEFORE_EACH_TEST_METHOD)` and transactional rollback.
- Use `@WithMockUser` to exercise secured controller paths.
- Drive endpoint behavior through `MockMvcRequestBuilders` and assert status + JSON payload fields.
- Seed test entities with `TestDataUtil` factory methods and persist through service/repository.
- Keep test names verbose and behavior-driven (`testThat...` naming style).
